name: Jane
description:
Things to remember:

• the way my best friend used to hug me
• the way of her poetic mind
• how we emailed each other every day despite our often meetings
• how we laughed at jokes that no one else understood except us
• unlimited freedom to create whatever we wanted


The series «Things to remember» is about my try to connect memories and pictures of it or see the shift between it.
2000-2015
